Package: keyoverlay
Version: 0~git
Architecture: armhf
Maintainer: tslmy <tslmy@users.noreply.github.com>
Depends: libc6
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Description: On-screen keymap overlay for SHARP Brain devices
 Listens to the keyboard and, while a modifier key is held, draws the
 matching key legend layout on the display. Supports both framebuffer
 (bare TUI console) and X11 backends.
 .
 https://github.com/tslmy/sharp-brain-keyboard-overlay
